  Locus:
    Page: 92
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Depression/Despair
---
Whenever you feel dissatisfied with life and the way things are going ...
if we just wait a little while, we will eventually see that the way God is
doing things is the right way, the best way, and (in the final analysis)
the only way.
